@startuml High-Level Workflow
'==============================================================================
'  VerdictCouncil — High-Level Hearing-Preparation Workflow
'  UML 2.5 Activity Diagram (clause 15: Activities)
'  Notation in use:
'    - Initial node            (filled circle ●)
'    - Action node             (rounded rectangle)
'    - Decision / merge node   (diamond)
'    - Fork / join node        (thick black bar)
'    - Activity partition      (swimlane)
'    - Activity final node     (◉ — successful completion)
'    - Flow final node         (⊗ — terminates *this* flow only, e.g. halt/cancel)
'    - Object node             (object name : Class) for `CaseState` data flow
'    - Note                    (descriptive callout)
'==============================================================================

title VerdictCouncil — High-Level Hearing-Preparation Workflow\n//UML 2.5 Activity Diagram//

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #F4E8E8
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #7B1E2A
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #7B1E2A
skinparam PartitionBorderColor #7B1E2A
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam DefaultFontName "EB Garamond"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 12

|#FFFFFF|Judge (Actor)|
start
:Authenticate (cookie JWT);
:Create case + upload documents
via OpenAI Files API;
:POST /cases/{id}/process;

|#FAFAFA|FastAPI api-service|
:Enqueue arq job
(`pipeline_jobs` outbox);
:Open SSE stream
(snapshot + heartbeat);

|#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
:**intake** (gpt-5-mini)
parse parties, domain, complexity;
note right
  ObjectFlow: writes
  CaseState.intake : IntakeOutput
end note

|#FFFFFF|Judge (Actor)|
if (Gate 1 — Intake review) then ([advance])
else if ([rerun])
  |#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
  :Re-enter intake via
  graph.update_state(past_config);
  end
else ([halt])
  end
endif

|#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
:**research_dispatch** node
(reset `research_parts`);
fork
  :**research-evidence**
  evidence_items, credibility_scores;
fork again
  :**research-facts**
  facts, timeline;
fork again
  :**research-witnesses**
  witnesses + credibility;
fork again
  :**research-law**
  PAIR + vector fallback;
end fork
:**research_join**
merge_dict by scope;
note right
  ObjectFlow: writes
  CaseState.research_output : ResearchOutput
end note

|#FFFFFF|Judge (Actor)|
if (Gate 2 — Research review) then ([advance])
else if ([rerun subagent])
  |#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
  :Fork from past_config
  with `Overwrite({})` on
  research_parts scope;
  end
else ([dispute fact])
  |#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
  :Append `judge_correction`
  to extra_instructions;
  end
endif

|#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
:**synthesis** (gpt-5)
IRAC arguments + uncertainty flags;
note right
  ObjectFlow: writes
  CaseState.synthesis : SynthesisOutput
end note

|#FFFFFF|Judge (Actor)|
if (Gate 3 — Synthesis review) then ([advance])
else ([rerun | edit question])
  |#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
  :Fork from past_config;
  end
endif

|#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
:**auditor** (gpt-5, ZERO tools)
fairness · citation · completeness;
note right
  ObjectFlow: writes
  CaseState.audit : AuditOutput
end note

|#FFFFFF|Judge (Actor)|
if (Gate 4 — Audit review) then ([advance])
  :Record `judicial_decision`
  with `ai_engagements`
  (agree/disagree + reason);
else if ([send_back])
  |#F4E8E8|arq-worker (LangGraph StateGraph)|
  :graph.update_state to target_phase
  + invoke(None, fork_config);
  end
else ([halt])
  end
endif

|#FAFAFA|FastAPI api-service|
:SSE terminal event
(completed | halted | failed | cancelled);

stop

legend right
  | Symbol | Meaning |
  | ● | Initial node |
  | ◉ | Activity final (`stop`) |
  | ⊗ | Flow final (`end`) — terminates this flow |
  | ◇ | Decision / merge |
  | ▬▬▬ | Fork / join |
  | □ | Action |
endlegend

footer //All gates persist to PostgresSaver after every node; SSE bridges from astream chunks; LangSmith auto-traces every agent and tool call.//
@enduml
